root.str:
The Eye of Kronos are the peacekeeping arm of the Terran Republic, with the aim of returning the Republics citizens safely back to Earth. Scientists within the Eye of Kronos work diligently around the clock in attempt to realise this goal.

Applies a decal to your armor or vehicle. TR use only.

Extra plating on this armor protects the wearer from debris and jagged edges when exploring and researching in physically hazardous areas.

This armor can only be worn by Human Heavy Assault troopers.
Grants the "Son of Dawn" prefix title.
Grants the "Daughter of Dawn" prefix title.

Designed with storage in mind for expedition personnel who maintain the tools, technology and Operatives used by Nascent Expeditions.

This armor can only be worn by Human Engineers.

Daughters of Dawn are an unintentional by-product of Nanite Systems' experiments of melding human consciousness with machine. Rumoured to be led by Sparrow Dawn, daughter of former Nanite Systems CEO Sasha Dawn. There is no solid evidence of their existence, however from time to time, their insignia can be found. A lot of the time, it doesn't take long for this graffiti to be removed not long after its discovery.

Unlocks a banner for your profile. NSO use only.

It's anniversary month and PlanetSide 2 turns 12 years old!

To kick off the month we had the Extra Life Game Day!

This years anniversary bundles* are themed around the lore of Auraxis and it's inhabitants, featuring a wide array of cosmetics for your characters in the form of:
  • Banners
  • Banner Frames
  • Decals
  • Knives
  • Titles
  • Infantry Armor and Helmet


Throughout the month we hope you look forward to Thanksgiving, Black Friday and Cyber Monday sales!

Oh and we merged Cobalt and Miller servers. You're welcome!
*12th Anniversary Bundles will be launched on 20th November 2024.
Unlocks a profile banner for your character. NC use only.

Lightweight armour for use when personnel are required to delve into caves and other subterranean features of Indar.

This armor can only be worn by Human Infiltrators.

NS Operatives who join Nascent Expeditions are fitted with heads that are fully enclosed to reduce the wear and tear of components when surveying the unforgiving wastelands of Indar. The fabric is designed to reduce potential overheating when the sun is at it's highest.

Wearable by all classes. All factions can use this gear.

The wastelands of Indar are harsh and unforgiving. Personnel in the medical field are equipped with a range of first gear and temperature controlled anti-biotics and pain killers for those unfortunate to succumb to illness on expeditions.

This armor can only be worn by Human Combat Medics.
A versatile knife with a razor sharp true-edge and a serrated false edge. A very useful tool for any Justiciar looking to gain intel from stubborn suspects.

The Eye of Kronos follow a strict interpretation of the rule of law. On the surface, it's population will say that the Justiciars and Artbiters are fair and just when it comes to dispensing justice. Others believe they keep the Republics' citizens in check with fear tactics, making examples of those unfortunate enough to be caught up in the justice system. However, this is just hearsay spread by enemies of the Republic.

Unlocks a banner for your profile. TR use only.
Grants the "Child of Dawn" prefix title.
Celebrate 12 years of war on Auraxis with these special items!
Celebrate twelve years of PlanetSide 2 with this limited bundle!

Lightweight armour with a thruster to aid personnel when exploring high locations. It is strongly recommended to be mindful when using the thruster to avoid damaging artefacts.

This armor can only be worn by Human Light Assault troopers.
Unlocks a profile banner for your character. TR use only.

Celebrate twelve years of PlanetSide 2 with this massive bundle. Note: Bundle contains weapons and cosmetics for VS/NC/TR/NSO empires. Heroic Boost is granted only to the character that purchases the bundle.

Formed in the early days of the Terran Republic as an advocacy group for veterans, reacclimating to a post-war world. In time, the organization's focus broadened, attracting civilian firearms enthusiasts and private security firms. The Crows were the first to bristle against the martial law imposed by the Republic. The Auraxis War is not an ideological battle for the Crows, just the thrill of the fight and cashing bonus checks.

Unlocks a banner for your profile. NC use only.

A structural prototype of a programmable blade by VEX Biologics for use with NS Operatives. Although the electronices and software don't function in this model, the design of this knife alone can cause horrific damage to its victim.

A gold etching based on similar artwork discovered on Earth painted by members of the Sumerian civilization. Anu "Seekers" will sometimes congregate under The Ziggurat on Hossin where they will examine and study relics of the Ancients.

Unlocks a banner for your profile. VS use only.
Celebrating 12 Years of War on Auraxis!

The wastelands of Indar are harsh and unforgiving. Operatives in the medical field are equipped with a range of first gear and some temperature controlled anti-biotics and pain killers for their human counter-parts who may succumb to illness on expeditions.

This armor can only be worn by NSO Combat Medics.

Lightweight armour for use when Operatives need to delve into caves and other subterranean features. Best used on a lightweight chassis to reduce any mishaps recovering the unit.

This armor can only be worn by NSO Infiltrators.
Unlocks a profile banner for your character. VS use only.

NS Operatives that are caught with this insignia sprayed anywhere on their chassis, whether intentional or not, are taken for an appraisal on their work ethic. In most cases human operators who have undergone these appraisals have their employment terminated shortly after. Those who have been discharged from the NS Operative program due to bearing this insignia have never been seen or heard from again.

Applies a decal to your armor or vehicle. NSO use only.

Extra plating on this armor protects the operative from debris and jagged edges when exploring and researching in physically hazardous areas.

This armor can only be worn by NSO Heavy Assault troopers.
Squad must have at least 2 members, a description and be public to enable recruitment

Designed to aid expedition teams who spend prolonged periods of time in the unforgiving wasteland of Indar. The face is fully concealed to protect from sandstorms and the blistering heat. The helmet is also equipped with breathing apparatus and light adaptive photoreceptors to enhance to wearers vision when the sun is at it's highest.

Wearable by all classes. All factions can use this gear.

The Sept of Anu believe mankind are direct descendants of the god-king Anu, who they believe visited Earth in prehistory, with his divine progeny, the Vanu. Their symbol is adopted from the ancient Sumerian symbol "dingir" which represents four staves in a starburst pattern.

Applies a decal to your armor or vehicle. VS use only.

Designed with storage in mind for Operatives who maintain the tools and technology used by Nascent Expeditions ...and also themselves.

This armor can only be worn by NSO Engineers.

Celebrate twelve years of PlanetSide 2 with this special bundle. Note: Bundle contains weapons and cosmetics for VS/NC/TR/NSO empires. Heroic Boost is granted only to the character that purchases the bundle.

The Legion of the Crows are a corporate mercenary splinter faction of the New Conglomerate. Their Motto: "Serve no master beyond your own desire." They are corporately sponsored by Arcenul Holdings, Woodman Alliance and a handful of undisclosed benefactors. While some of their funding sources maybe questionable, their fraternal allegience with the NC is not.

Applies a decal to your armor or vehicle. NC use only.
This knife is given to Anunnaki Zealots who pass the trials set by the Sept of Anu.
Unlocks a profile banner for your character. NSO use only.

Lightweight armour with a thruster to aid Operatives when exploring high locations. It is strongly recommended to be mindful when using the thruster to avoid damaging artefacts.

This armor can only be worn by NSO Light Assault troopers.
Applies a loyalty decal to your armor or vehicle, celebrating twelve years of PlanetSide 2
Genudine Multiplanetary originally manufactured this knife for Private Military Contractor "Osprey Defense". The lightweight and robust design proved very popular amongst the PMC group.
